{
  "info": {
    "name": "Movie Ticket Booking System",
    "description": "API Collection สำหรับทดสอบ Movie Ticket Booking System\n\n## วิธีใช้\n1. Import ไฟล์นี้เข้า Postman\n2. ตั้งค่า Environment Variable `baseUrl` = `http://localhost:5000`\n3. รัน Register หรือ Login ก่อน — Token จะถูก Set อัตโนมัติ\n4. ทดสอบ Route อื่นๆ ได้เลย",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "movieId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "showtimeId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "seatId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
